  "title": "Decadent Dutch Smoked Salmon Hash",
  "description": "A keto-friendly twist on a classic Dutch dish, featuring smoked salmon and a rich, jammy deglaze, served in a traditional molcajete vessel.",
  "cuisine": "Dutch",
